caption.p: Histology of ovaries in adults of Glyphodes pyloalis emerging from untreated ( a) and treated larvae by Artemisia annua floral essential oil ( b). In treatments of the ovarian sheath significant changes and yolk granules were reduced under the influence of vacuolization in cytoplasm compared to the control. ( FE) follicular epithelium, ( V) vacuole, and ( Y) yolk granules.
